com.mapbox.services.commons.geojson

Class GeometryCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.services.commons.geojson.GeometryCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeoJSON

    public class GeometryCollection
extends Object
implements GeoJSON
    A GeoJSON object with the type "GeometryCollection" is a geometry object which represents a collection of geometry objects.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Official GeoJSON GeometryCollection Specifications
